Cave Canem Subscriber Requires:
- libmysql++ and libmysqlclient
- NDDS 4.5c
- Boost 1.38

The creation of a database is also required. Database information can be
edited in /etc/cavecanem/cavecanem_subscriber.xml.


Installation Instructions:

$ ./configure --sysconfdir=/etc --prefix=/usr

NOTE: It is recomended to install Cave Canem adding --sysconfdir=/etc and 
--prefix=/usr to configure script if init.d scripts are going to be used.

$ make

# make install
